headline: Appointment of Yves Decadt as Member of Poxel’s Board of Directors
summary: LYON, France, October 31, 2025--Regulatory News: POXEL SA (Euronext : POXEL - FR0012432516), a clinical stage biopharmaceutical company developing innovative treatments for chronic serious diseases with metabolic pathophysiology, including metabolic dysfunction-associated steatohepatitis (MASH) and rare metabolic disorders, today announces the appointment of Yves Decadt as a member of its Board of Directors.
